Class ObjectId

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.undercouch.bson4jackson.types.ObjectId

  • public class ObjectId
extends java.lang.Object
    A unique identifier for MongoDB documents. Such identifiers consist of a timestamp, a machine ID and a counter.
